#: views/onboarding/step1.html.twig:3
msgid "Welcome!"
msgstr "Bienvenue !"

#: views/onboarding/step1.html.twig:11
#, php-format
msgid "Welcome %s!"
msgstr "Bienvenue %s !"

#: views/onboarding/step1.html.twig:51
#, php-format
msgid "The few next screens will explain you some main features of %s."
msgstr ""
"Les écrans qui suivent vous expliqueront quelques-unes des principales "
"fonctionnalités de %s."

#: views/onboarding/step1.html.twig:55
#, php-format
msgid ""
"There’s not much to know before getting started with %s. This onboarding "
"should take less than 3 minutes of your time."
msgstr ""
"Il n’y a pas grand-chose à savoir avant de pouvoir utiliser %s. Cette "
"introduction devrait vous prendre moins de 3 minutes à parcourir."

#: views/onboarding/step1.html.twig:63
msgid "or skip the onboarding"
msgstr "ou passer l’introduction"

#: views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:3 views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:11
msgid "Read at your own pace"
msgstr "Lisez à votre rythme"

#: views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:15
msgid "The <strong>Reading</strong> tab helps you organise your reading list."
msgstr ""
"L’onglet <strong>Lecture</strong> vous aide à organiser votre liste de "
"lecture."

#: views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:20
msgid ""
"“News” gives you suggestions of what to read from the websites that you "
"follow."
msgstr ""
"Le « Journal » vous suggère des choses à lire depuis les sites que vous "
"suivez."

#: views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:24
msgid ""
"Short on time? “Bookmark” links to read later and find them in one click."
msgstr ""
"Vous manquez de temps ? Placez vos liens dans les « Signets » pour les lire "
"plus tard et les retrouver en un clic."

#: views/onboarding/step2.html.twig:28
msgid ""
"Finally, keep track of the links you have already read in the “Links read” "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, gardez une trace des liens que vous avez déjà lus depuis la section "
"« Liens lus »."

#: views/onboarding/step3.html.twig:3 views/onboarding/step3.html.twig:11
msgid "Store your links"
msgstr "Stockez vos liens"

#: views/onboarding/step3.html.twig:15
msgid "<strong>My links</strong> organises your links into collections."
msgstr "<strong>Mes liens</strong> organisent vos liens en collections."

#: views/onboarding/step3.html.twig:20
msgid ""
"All the links you want to be able to find easily have their place in the "
"collections."
msgstr ""
"Tous les liens que vous souhaitez retrouver facilement plus tard ont leur "
"place dans les collections."

#: views/onboarding/step3.html.twig:24
msgid ""
"By default, you start with 2 collections: <strong>“My favorites” and “My "
"shares”.</strong> Obviously, you can create as many thematic collections as "
"you want!"
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, vous démarrez avec 2 collections : <strong>« Mes favoris » et "
"« Mes partages ».</strong> Vous pouvez évidemment créer autant de "
"collections thématiques que vous voulez !"

#: views/onboarding/step4.html.twig:3 views/onboarding/step4.html.twig:11
msgid "Follow content from Internet"
msgstr "Suivez le contenu d’Internet"

#: views/onboarding/step4.html.twig:15
msgid ""
"The <strong>Feeds</strong> list the websites and collections that you follow."
msgstr ""
"Les <strong>Flux</strong> listent les sites et les collections que vous "
"suivez."

#: views/onboarding/step4.html.twig:20
#, php-format
msgid ""
"A lot of websites can be followed in %s <strong>as long as they offer a Web "
"feed</strong>: most news sites, blogs, podcasts… Even YouTube channels!"
msgstr ""
"Beaucoup de sites peuvent être suivis dans %s <strong>tant qu’ils proposent "
"un flux Web</strong> : la plupart des sites d’actualités, les blogs, les "
"podcasts… Même les chaînes YouTube !"

#: views/onboarding/step4.html.twig:25
msgid ""
"This is perfect if you want to be notified when new content is published "
"without wasting time checking each website individually."
msgstr ""
"C’est parfait si vous souhaitez être averti⋅e lorsque de nouveaux contenus "
"sont publiés sans perdre de temps à vérifier chaque site un par un."

#: views/onboarding/step5.html.twig:3 views/onboarding/step5.html.twig:11
msgid "Share with the rest of Internet"
msgstr "Partagez avec le reste d’Internet"

#: views/onboarding/step5.html.twig:15
msgid ""
"The <strong>Profile</strong> is your public page listing all what you share."
msgstr ""
"Le <strong>Profil</strong> est la page publique qui répertorie tout ce que "
"vous partagez."

#: views/onboarding/step5.html.twig:20
msgid ""
"Every time you share a link in a public collection, it gets added to your "
"profile. <strong>Annotate your reading to add a personal touch.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Chaque fois que vous partagez un lien dans une collection publique, il "
"apparaîtra dans votre profil. <strong>Annotez vos lectures pour y ajouter "
"une touche personnelle.</strong>"

#: views/onboarding/step5.html.twig:24
msgid "Nothing like spreading the address to your Flus profile around!"
msgstr "Rien de tel que de diffuser l’adresse de votre profil autour de vous !"

#: views/onboarding/step6.html.twig:3 views/onboarding/step6.html.twig:11
msgid "Start exploring 🚀"
msgstr "Commencez à explorer 🚀"

#: views/onboarding/step6.html.twig:15
#, php-format
msgid ""
"This is the end of the onboarding. You should now have the keys to use %s in "
"an efficient way."
msgstr ""
"C’est la fin de cette introduction. Vous devriez maintenant avoir tous les "
"éléments en main pour utiliser %s de manière efficace."

#: views/onboarding/step6.html.twig:19
msgid "However, you still have things to discover, so stay curious!"
msgstr ""
"Il vous reste cependant encore des choses à découvrir, restez donc curieux "
"ou curieuse !"

